metadata.name: Chasing Freedom
metadata.description:
Chasing birbs on a broom stick

A bit of a deviation from my usual painting style. 
Letting go of the constrants set by lines to focus on more organic and textured brush strokes. 

A breath of fresh air!
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
Original illustration by Runbo
4294 x 3289
